{"tid":1309344,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你地會唔會打比HR？","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T13:32:02.000Z","uid":84117,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"26b9f3745e91c528c33a7e1482c94f13383db258","tid":1309344,"uid":84117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"大家有冇試過比人hold起offer？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日同新公司HR傾好晒人工、福利, 咁對方都好自然問我幾時返得工, 我就想放多一個禮拜假同朋友去個旅行, 所以就over one month notice<br />\n<br />\n之後佢話要同部門主管夾下, 再覆返我下星期幾時簽約. 咁ge情況, 如果佢真係好急要人, 有冇機會hold起我個offer? 如果hold起左, 係咪循例都會通知聲?<br />\n<br />\n大家又有冇試過打電話比HR?<br />\n我宜家係咪只可以耐心等候? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b15944f31cc92c2e76ffe55ca7460f82b70eb04","tid":1309344,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"打去問啦<br />\nover one month notice<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9bd209993cd3995c0fde71c059ef1651d11514","tid":1309344,"uid":84117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b15944f31cc92c2e76ffe55ca7460f82b70eb04","tid":1309344,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"打去問啦<br />\nover one month notice<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:12:22.000Z","msg":"會唔會覺得我好chur<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38cb27cf4cc6d1a90681e88caf309e499ced3e0","tid":1309344,"uid":24079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b9f3745e91c528c33a7e1482c94f13383db258","tid":1309344,"uid":84117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:04:27.000Z","msg":"大家有冇試過比人hold起offer？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日同新公司HR傾好晒人工、福利, 咁對方